title: For Sale/Trade:  Custom Caspian 1911 by Doug Jones
postcontent:
This is an original Doug Jones custom Caspian Government 1911 ground-up build. It features a Caspian slide and frame with a black/od green cerakote, checkered back strap, competition rail job by Acc-U-Rail, hand fitted Kart NM barrel and bushing, guide rod recoil system, extended safety, slide release and mag release button, Wilson Combat internals with a 2.5 lb competition trigger, Kensight Adjustable sights, VZ Grips, and two 8-round mags. This pistol is as good as it gets in the accuracy department. Looks plain Jane but will out shoot any factory custom on the market, including the popular high priced guns. The gun is worth over $3000 and has only been fired for testing. Doug Jones is a well known professional gunsmith who builds and services nationally known competition organization guns on a regular basis and inherited the rights to the ACC-U-RAIL system which is widely used on the competition circuit. The accurail is a design feature that runs the length of the slide, taking up any play in the slide's movement to improve accuracy and give the gun a solid, tight fit versus the traditionally loose frame/slide fit on most 1911s. If you are looking for a real sleeper (and a pretty one) that will make your buddies jealous, this is it.
Build includes:
Caspian Slide (Black Cerakote Caspian Frame (OD Green Cerakote)
5" Kart National Match barrel and bushings
Extended Mag Release
Kensights adjustable sights
Wilson Combat internals and trigger
VZ grips
Doug Jones Accurail
